30
00:03:21,199 --> 00:03:22,919
MAN OVER RADIO:
...flying from the US to control that...

31
00:03:23,079 --> 00:03:26,439
- (CHILDREN SHOUTING)
- (MAN SHOUTS)

32
00:03:31,879 --> 00:03:34,959
(MAN CACKLES PLAYFULLY)

33
00:03:36,879 --> 00:03:38,559
Can we get some ice cream?

34
00:03:38,719 --> 00:03:41,239
- No, we gotta go.
- You always say no.

35
00:03:41,399 --> 00:03:44,359
- Well, are you gonna buy?
- No, you buy.

36
00:03:44,519 --> 00:03:45,959
OK, what are
we getting today?

37
00:03:46,119 --> 00:03:49,399
- Passion fruit.
- OK, passion fruit.

38
00:03:49,599 --> 00:03:51,799
(CHILDREN CLAMORING)

39
